## KOHA DOCUMENTATION

**SERVER** 

AIC library database KOHA is hosted at AWE (Amazon Web Services) on N. Virginia Region using EC2. [here](http://aws.amazon.com/).


**HOW TO CHANGE THE WEBSITE** 

In order to change the library website, you have to login from 

http://ec2-54-145-21-234.compute-1.amazonaws.com:8080/cgi-bin/koha/mainpage.pl?logout.x=1

Click **Administration** => **System Preferences**

To change the left navigation in the page search for
 
**OpacHeader** -- Header

**OpacNav** -- Left Navigation

**OpacNavRight** -- Right Navigation




Read koha documents here:

http://manual.koha-community.org/3.2/en/impopac.html

Watch this tutorial for more detail:

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GPmdJnqxYZI